query:
SELECT
                (SELECT COUNT(*)
                FROM booking
                WHERE
                    time_to >= ?1 AND
                    MAX(time_from, ?1) < MIN(time_to, ?2) AND
                    (canceled_at IS NULL OR canceled_at > ?4) AND
                    unit_id = ?3) +
                (SELECT COUNT(*)
                FROM adhoc_reservation
                WHERE
                    time_to >= ?1 AND
                    MAX(time_from, ?1) < MIN(time_to, ?2) AND
                    (deleted_at IS NULL OR deleted_at > ?4) AND
                    unit_id = ?3)
                AS "count"
